{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemetextinputcomponenttokensprovider"]}],"kind":"symbol","relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllTextInputComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent09TextInputB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s9EscapableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"title":"Conforms To","kind":"relationships"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for input text component tokens","    \/\/ by inheriting from existing provider","    class CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider: OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider {","","        \/\/ Then override the text input component tokens you want.","","        override var sizeMaxWidth: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._3000 }","","        override var spacePaddingBlockDefault: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSmall }","","        override var colorBorderEnabled: MultipleColorSemanticToken { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","","        override var borderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthMedium}","","        \/\/ ...","    }","","    \/\/ Or define your own provider from scratch","    class CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider: TextInputComponentTokens {","","        \/\/ And implement hunders of tokens.","        \/\/ You are allowed to give semantic tokens providers if you want to define values.","    }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Then, you can give this "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" to your own theme implementation:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class LocalTheme: OrangeTheme {","","    override init() {","        super.init(textInput: CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider())","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"or to an already existing theme for example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    OrangeTheme(textInput: CustomTextInputComponentTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is also possible to use your own semantic tokens providers for this component tokens providers:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["    \/\/ Uses by default here:","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSizeSemanticTokensProvider for sizes","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeColorSemanticTokensProvider for colors","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeBorderSemanticTokensProvider for borders","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeSpaceSemanticTokensProvider for spaces","    \/\/ - OrangeThemeDimensionSemanticTokensProvider for dimensions","    let inputTextComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider()","","    \/\/ Or use your own size, border, color, space and _ semantic tokens providers (or only some)","    let inputTextComponentTokensProvider = OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider(","                                                sizes: CustomSizeSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                borders: CustomBorderSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                colors: CustomColorSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                space: CustomSpaceSemanticTokensProvider(),","                                                dimensions: CustomDimensionSemanticTokensProvider())"],"syntax":"swift"},{"name":"Since","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.17.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of input text","type":"text"}]},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"input text","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTextInput"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllTextInputComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"TextInputComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"input text","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Inout text","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of colors ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"borders (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and  dimensions (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/init(sizes:borders:colors:spaces:dimensions:)"],"title":"Initializers","generated":true},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/borders","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/colors","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/dimensions","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/sizes","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/spaces"],"title":"Instance Properties","generated":true},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeTextInputComponentTokensProvider\/TextInputComponentTokens-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\